                    <p class="modal-icon-text soil" id="modal-icon-text-title">
                        <strong>TIERRA SANDY LOAM</strong>
                    </p>
                    <p class="modal-icon-text soil-text">A sandy loam with significant amounts of calcareous shale. Free draining with moderate to low nutrient availability. Vines show reduced vigor, with lower yields and earlier ripening than in other blocks.</p>

