                    <p class="modal-icon-text wine" id="modal-icon-text-title"> <strong> WINES </strong></p>
                    <p class="modal-icon-text wine-text"> These blocks make stunning Pinot Noir, rivaling our coveted Morrito in quality. This is where the core of the Califa Pinot Noir comes from. Very concentrated, with red fruit flavors that are more focused than the black fruit and spice of Morrito.</p>
